cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically in the areas of 3D object detection and SLAM. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization and machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel measurement function, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves geometric constraints, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
